high_descs: Turn to your left and walk partly to make a quick right to have the counter in front of you.
Go towards the counter and pick up the spoon on the counter.
Turn left and then a right so you are in front of the sink.
Place the spoon in the sink next to the egg. Turn on the water and then turn it off and take out the spoon.
Open the first drawer on the right and place the spoon inside and shut it.
anns.task_desc: Clean the spoon to put it in the drawer.

high_descs: Turn left and walk straight ahead. Turn right to face the sink.
Pick up the spoon to the right of the sink
Place the spoon inside of the sink.
Turn the faucet on so water fills the sink. Turn off the faucet and pick up the spoon.
Turn left and open the small wooden drawer in front of the watermelon
Place the spoon inside of the drawer and close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Find and clean a spoon then place inside of a drawer.

high_descs: Walk to the spoon on the counter to the left of the stove top.
Pick up the spoon from the counter top.
Move slightly left to the sink.
Clean the spoon in the sink.
Turn left to face the drawers.
Open the drawer to the left of the vegetable and put the spoon in it.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spoon inside a drawer.
